</paragraph>
<paragraph id="663E369ADD1F5A36FF7AFD87CF52CC2C" blockId="29.[227,1436,552,614]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Tortonian of 
<collectingCountry id="1E96760ADD1F5A36FEE4FD87CDF6CC08" box="[381,464,552,578]" name="Greece" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Greece</collectingCountry>
(Messara Basin, 
<collectingRegion id="A445F878DD1F5A36FD07FD87CEF9CC08" box="[670,735,552,578]" country="Greece" name="Kriti" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Crete</collectingRegion>
) (this work) and Piacenzian (Pliocene) of 
<collectingCountry id="1E96760ADD1F5A36FB4AFD87C901CC08" box="[1235,1319,552,578]" name="Turkey" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Turkey</collectingCountry>
(Antakya Basin, Samandag Fm.) (see 
<bibRefCitation id="02104B6BDD1F5A36FDB2FDE3CEF8CC2C" author="Tari U. &amp; Tuysuz O. &amp; Can Genc S. &amp; Imren C. &amp; Blackwell B. A. B. &amp; Lom N. &amp; Tekesin O. &amp; Uskuplu S. &amp; Erel L. &amp; Altiok S. &amp; Beyhan M." box="[555,734,587,614]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" pagination="27 - 55" refId="ref32003" refString="Tari U., Tuysuz O., Can Genc S., Imren C., Blackwell B. A. B., Lom N., Tekesin O., Uskuplu S., Erel L., Altiok S. &amp; Beyhan M. 2013. The geology and morphology of the Antakya Graben between the Amik Triple Junction and the Cyprus Arc. Geodinamica Acta 26 (1 - 2): 27 - 55. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 09853111.2013.858962" type="journal article" year="2013">
Tarı 
<emphasis id="54F5EA88DD1F5A36FDFBFDE3CEBACC2F" box="[610,668,587,613]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">et al.</emphasis>
2013
</bibRefCitation>
for the age).
</paragraph>
